pd_0_com_0text: You opened the door! Great! Now I will look for my dad... Even if we're both ghosts now, I'd like too see him again...
pd_1_com_0text: I am glad I could help.
pd_1_com_1text: Your dad was a kind person...
pd_3_com_0text: I am happy to be your friend.
pd_5_com_0text: Now I can give you some magical stuff my dad was working with. I have a weird hat: dad told me that everyone believes you when you put it on. Or, I can give you these super goggles that let you see monster's health precisely.
pd_6_com_0text: I'll take the weird hat; I like to be the life of the party.
pd_6_com_1text: I'll take the goggles. I'll be stronger with them.
pd_7_com_0text: Wait! Before you go... The last chapter of the story of the princess is lost... But I would like to know how you would have ended it. If you could choose, how would you end the story?
pd_8_com_0text: She builds a wonderful castle and everyone reveres her.
pd_8_com_1text: She finds the evil mage that imprisoned her and she defeats him.
pd_8_com_2text: She runs away and goes on an endless adventure, exploring the stars.
pd_9_com_0text: Woah, I'd love to visit that palace! What a nice ending for the story!
pd_11_com_0text: A warrior princess, that's cool! I love your ending to the story!
pd_12_com_0text: Up to the sky and beyond! I'd love to fly through the stars... What a great ending!
pd_13_com_0text: Great choice! Bye bye kind stranger, thank you for your help!
